name: Front-end Coders - July Online Meetup
description:
Join us for an online meetup to talk about the front-end world and a few interesting topics!

# Topics
- An introduction to Cypress with Vue (Jordan Bienvenue)
- Do you think of accessibility when you build a website? ([guest speaker] Razvan Statescu AKA @the.dev.guy on Instagram)
- Open Discussions about Front-end Topics ( Sandeep )

Join on the following link:
https://meet.mscc.mu/FabulousFrontendFantasies

We only have simple rules:
- Kindly mute your mic when you're not speaking
- Use the chat to ask questions
- Be nice
- Be Friendly
- Be Courteous
